mendous reliability, something vital to surviving the punishing race. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cphoenix-picture\u003e\u003ca\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjEyNzQzNTAzODYzMDMxMzA1/1964-ferrari-250-lm.webp 380w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEyNzQzNTAzODYzMDMxMzA1/1964-ferrari-250-lm.webp 620w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEyNzQzNTAzODYzMDMxMzA1/1964-ferrari-250-lm.webp 700w\"/\u003e\u003csource sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjEyNzQzNTAzODYzMDMxMzA1/1964-ferrari-250-lm.png 380w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEyNzQzNTAzODYzMDMxMzA1/1964-ferrari-250-lm.png 620w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEyNzQzNTAzODYzMDMxMzA1/1964-ferrari-250-lm.png 700w\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"1964 Ferrari 250 LM \" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/t_share/MjEyNzQzNTAzODYzMDMxMzA1/1964-ferrari-250-lm.png\" data-src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEyNzQzNTAzODYzMDMxMzA1/1964-ferrari-250-lm.png\" height=\"672\" width=\"1024\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" itemprop=\"contentUrl url\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"caption\"\u003e1964 Ferrari 250 LM\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"author\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.hagerty.com/media/market-trends/hagerty-insider/ferrari-250-lm-that-won-le-mans-sells-for-36-3m/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eHagerty\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eDriven by Masten Gregory and Jochen Rindt, the Ferrari 250 LM chassis number 5893 solidified its position in racing history when it took the overall win at Le Mans in 1965, which was made even more significant by the fact that it was the last time Ferrari would secure the overall victory at the most legendary automotive endurance race.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cphoenix-super-link href=\"https://www.autoblog.com/news/an-authentic-1967-mustang-gt500-surfaces-on-bring-a-trailer\" onclick=\"return window.phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" phx-track-id=\"Embed Card Click\"\u003e\u003c/phoenix-super-link\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"a-racing-legend-now-an-auction-legend\"\u003eA racing legend, now an auction legend\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eFollowing its 1965 Le Mans win, the 250 LM raced at the 24 Hours of Daytona in 1966 and 1968. It headed back to the 24 Hours of Le Mans that same year and again in 1969. Its final race took place at the 1970 24 Hours of Daytona before N.A.R.T. team owner Luigi Chinetti ended up selling the 250 LM in 1970. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv phx-gallery=\"\"\u003e\u003cphx-gallery-image data-caption-html=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;1964 Ferrari 250 LM\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\" data-full-height=\"1334\" data-full-src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_2000%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_2000/MjEyNzQzNDE0NzQyMDAxMjgw/2023-amelia-concours-best-in-show-0004a-deremer-studios-llc-scaled-1.jpg\" data-full-width=\"2000\" data-image-id=\"ci02f3d10250012609\" data-image-slug=\"2023-Amelia-Concours-Best-in-Show-0004A-Deremer-Studios-LLC-scaled-1\" data-public-id=\"MjEyNzQzNDE0NzQyMDAxMjgw\" data-title=\"1964 Ferrari 250 LM\"\u003e\u003c/phx-gallery-image\u003e\u003cphx-gallery-image data-caption-html=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;1964 Ferrari 250 LM\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\" data-full-height=\"679\" data-full-src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Ch_2000%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_2000/MjEyNzQzNTAzODYzMDk2ODQx/screenshot-2025-02-10-132852.png\" data-full-width=\"1021\" data-image-id=\"ci02f3d11720002680\" data-image-slug=\"Screenshot 2025-02-10 132852\" data-public-id=\"MjEyNzQzNTAzODYzMDk2ODQx\" data-title=\"1964 Ferrari 250 LM\"\u003e\u003c/phx-gallery-image\u003e\u003cphx-gallery-image data-caption-html=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;1964 Ferrari 250 LM\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\" data-full-height=\"683\" data-full-src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_2000%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_2000/MjEyNzQzNDE0NzQyMDAxMTYx/2023-amelia-concours-best-in-show-0009a-deremer-studios-llc-scaled-1-1024x683.jpg\" data-full-width=\"1024\" data-image-id=\"ci02f3d10250002609\" data-image-slug=\"2023-Amelia-Concours-Best-in-Show-0009A-Deremer-Studios-LLC-scaled-1-1024x683\" data-public-id=\"MjEyNzQzNDE0NzQyMDAxMTYx\" data-title=\"1964 Ferrari 250 LM\"\u003e\u003c/phx-gallery-image\u003e\u003cphx-gallery-image data-caption-html=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;1964 Ferrari 250 LM\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\" data-full-height=\"683\" data-full-src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_2000%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_2000/MjEyNzQzNDE0NDczNTY1NzA1/2023-amelia-concours-best-in-show-0012a-deremer-studios-llc-scaled-1-1024x683.jpg\" data-full-width=\"1024\" data-image-id=\"ci02f3d10240002680\" data-image-slug=\"2023-Amelia-Concours-Best-in-Show-0012A-Deremer-Studios-LLC-scaled-1-1024x683\" data-public-id=\"MjEyNzQzNDE0NDczNTY1NzA1\" data-title=\"1964 Ferrari 250 LM\"\u003e\u003c/phx-gallery-image\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"1964-ferrari-250-lm\"\u003e1964 Ferrari 250 LM\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003e1964 Ferrari 250 LM\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/ar_16:9%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_406%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEyNzQzNDE0NzQyMDAxMjgw/2023-amelia-concours-best-in-show-0004a-deremer-studios-llc-scaled-1.jpg\" alt=\"2023-Amelia-Concours-Best-in-Show-0004A-Deremer-Studios-LLC-scaled-1\" itemprop=\"image\" loading=\"lazy\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe car was then retired from racing and passed on to the Indianapolis Motor Speedway Museum. The victorious 250 LM was displayed in the museum and also traveled to Pebble Beach and Amelia Island, where it unsurprisingly won the illustrious Best in Show Concours de Sport in 2023. After over half a century, the Museum decided to sell the 250 LM to help improve its existing collection and restoration efforts.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cphoenix-picture\u003e\u003ca\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjEyNzQzNzU1MTE4MzU2MDk2/1964-ferrari-250-lm.webp 380w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEyNzQzNzU1MTE4MzU2MDk2/1964-ferrari-250-lm.webp 620w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEyNzQzNzU1MTE4MzU2MDk2/1964-ferrari-250-lm.webp 700w\"/\u003e\u003csource sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjEyNzQzNzU1MTE4MzU2MDk2/1964-ferrari-250-lm.png 380w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEyNzQzNzU1MTE4MzU2MDk2/1964-ferrari-250-lm.png 620w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEyNzQzNzU1MTE4MzU2MDk2/1964-ferrari-250-lm.png 700w\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"1964 Ferrari 250 LM\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/t_share/MjEyNzQzNzU1MTE4MzU2MDk2/1964-ferrari-250-lm.png\" data-src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEyNzQzNzU1MTE4MzU2MDk2/1964-ferrari-250-lm.png\" height=\"941\" width=\"1435\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" itemprop=\"contentUrl url\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"caption\"\u003e1964 Ferrari 250 LM\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"author\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFerrari\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eChassis 5893 is the most significant Ferrari 250 LM ever sold and commanded $10 million over the expected price. In the final few minutes of the auction, prices soared past the target, and it took its place not only as the priciest 250 LM ever sold but also as the sixth \u003ca href=\"https://www.autoblog.com/features/most-expensive-cars-in-the-world\"\u003emost expensive car\u003c/a\u003e ever sold at auction. The buyer has not been named.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cphoenix-super-link href=\"https://www.autoblog.com/reviews/2025-ford-mustang-5-reasons-to-love-it-2-reasons-to-think-twice\" onclick=\"return window.phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" phx-track-id=\"Embed Card Click\"\u003e\u003c/phoenix-super-link\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"final-thoughts\"\u003eFinal thoughts\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eIt’s awesome to see a race car with such a legendary racing pedigree attain a stratospheric price. The 250 LM was the underdog of the race, but it proved to be the most resilient entry in the 1965 Le Mans endurance race. The fact that it changed hands from Ferrari to N.A.R.T. to the Indianapolis Motor Speedway Museum to the auction winner makes it even more appealing as a collector’s holy grail. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cphoenix-super-link href=\"https://www.autoblog.com/news/you-can-now-buy-this-obscure-ev-that-only-had-16-units-produced\" onclick=\"return window.phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" phx-track-id=\"Embed Card Click\"\u003e\u003c/phoenix-super-link\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/article\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003csection id=\"phximagetilehub-3\"\u003e\u003cphoenix-hub data-group-size=\"9\" data-first-group-size=\"9\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cphoenix-non-personalized-recommendations-no-tracking config=\"{\u0026#34;siteBasePath\u0026#34;:null,\u0026#34;size\u0026#34;:3,\u0026#34;widgetName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;tempestn_tile-hub_autoblog_article-page_title-not-found-1-1\u0026#34;}\"\u003e\u003c/phoenix-non-personalized-recommendations-no-tracking\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/phoenix-hub\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
